attributionInfo.brokerName: KELLER WILLIAMS ON THE WATER S
KELLER WILLIAMS ON THE WATER S

data.description: GREAT INVESTMENT! 52 times a year rental. Newly painted and carpet, Siesta key 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, Split plan condo. Deeded beach access within steps, Huge Lenai, enjoy watching sunsets and entertaining family and friends. Large bedrooms w/walk-in closets, laundry room in unit, heated pool, Three lighted tennis courts, clubhouse, his and her saunas and an exercise room.  Boat docks, fishing, kayaking   and    Weekly rentals are permitted - On-site rental office. Secure building, Plenty of guest parking.  Both bedrooms and the living room have sliding glass doors out to the balcony. Walk to restaurants, tiki bars and shopping. Great location easy to get on and off the key. Bright and clean unit with southern exposure.
